cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image reconstruction using deep learning techniques. Additionally, it may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it involves the use of neural networks for learning complex representations. The Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category is also a possibility as MRI images are a form of multimedia data. Finally, the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category may also be relevant as the proposed network architecture is inspired by the densely-connected neural network.
